Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.78,0:00:16.78,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,Subaru-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.27,0:00:39.10,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What happened? What the \Nhell is going on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.45,0:00:41.14,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,Subaru-kun, stay down.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.14,0:00:42.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We've lost our Windbreak protection!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.83,0:00:44.30,Default,Otto,0000,0000,0000,,You didn't know?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.30,0:00:48.63,Default,Otto,0000,0000,0000,,Only one being with such a huge \Nbody can fly through fog!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.92,0:00:50.90,Default,Otto,0000,0000,0000,,The White Whale!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.06,0:02:32.36,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Rem, do you see the White Whale?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.36,0:02:34.04,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,I cannot! It's too dark!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.30,0:02:36.49,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,What happened to the other carriages?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.49,0:02:38.22,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,They seem to have scattered.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.22,0:02:40.46,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,But I do not know where they have fled!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.46,0:02:41.45,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.45,0:02:44.19,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,After we finally found some transportation...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.93,0:02:51.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.07,0:03:02.93,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,Run past it, to the left!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.49,0:03:06.79,Default,Otto,0000,0000,0000,,Left, left, left, left, left, left, left!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.76,0:03:17.17,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,Eat this!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.98,0:03:25.26,Default,Otto,0000,0000,0000,,D-Did you get it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.68,0:03:30.59,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,It didn't work.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.59,0:03:33.16,Default,Otto,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-Why is it targeting us?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.16,0:03:35.76,Default,Otto,0000,0000,0000,,There are other carriages out there!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.76,0:03:38.70,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Complaining won't change anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.64,0:03:42.39,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Think... Think, think!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.39,0:03:43.60,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,We need a way out!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.60,0:03:46.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't there something? \NAnything, anything, anything?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.63,0:03:48.80,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,Subaru-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.88,0:03:51.81,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,Please accept this.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.81,0:03:53.61,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Did you come up with something?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.12,0:03:56.61,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,I shall get off the carriage and intercept it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.61,0:03:59.24,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,In the meantime, you escape the fog.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.24,0:04:03.43,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,Otto-sama, please take care of Subaru-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.43,0:04:05.54,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,He has the payment we promised you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.54,0:04:07.28,Default,Otto,0000,0000,0000,,P-Payment?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.28,0:04:08.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the least of our problems now!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.70,0:04:11.08,Default,Otto,0000,0000,0000,,We have to stay alive first!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.08,0:04:13.72,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,Subaru-kun, I am not very smart,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.72,0:04:15.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so this is the only plan I can think of.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.92,0:04:16.79,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,Please...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.79,0:04:18.70,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hold on, Rem!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.70,0:04:20.86,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,I won't let you! I won't let you go!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.86,0:04:24.03,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,If... If you also die, I'll...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.09,0:04:36.48,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,I believe I was born for this very moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.94,0:04:39.80,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talk—
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.92,0:04:44.46,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,What did you...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.06,0:04:47.49,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,It will be all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.49,0:04:51.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I shall be watching over\Nyou from behind, always.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.42,0:05:18.65,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Where's Rem?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.65,0:05:20.93,Default,Otto,0000,0000,0000,,Natsuki-san, you're awake?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.93,0:05:22.43,Default,Otto,0000,0000,0000,,Please don't move.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.43,0:05:24.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The ground dragon's still\Nrunning at full speed!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.54,0:05:27.12,Default,Otto,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have time to worry about you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.12,0:05:29.05,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,I don't care about that!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.05,0:05:31.10,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Where's Rem? What happened to Rem?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.63,0:05:34.10,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Answer me, Otto! What happened to Rem?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.45,0:05:39.40,Default,Otto,0000,0000,0000,,So we could escape,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.08,0:05:44.06,Default,Otto,0000,0000,0000,,she jumped out of the carriage \Nto intercept the White Whale.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.32,0:05:50.26,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Go back.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.26,0:05:51.21,Default,Otto,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.72,0:05:54.56,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,I said to go back! We have to...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.56,0:05:56.19,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,We have to save Rem!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.19,0:05:58.17,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Go back right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.22,0:06:01.57,Default,Otto,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What good will that do?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.57,0:06:05.33,Default,Otto,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't you see how terrifying that \Nmonster, the White Whale, is?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.33,0:06:06.64,Default,Otto,0000,0000,0000,,That would be suicide!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.64,0:06:09.01,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,I saw the monster up close!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.01,0:06:10.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I'm telling you to go back!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.67,0:06:14.28,Default,Otto,0000,0000,0000,,Have you gone insane?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.28,0:06:18.55,Default,Otto,0000,0000,0000,,You want to squander\Nthe hope that she left us?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.55,0:06:20.70,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you dare talk about Rem!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.70,0:06:22.20,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,You abandoned her...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.20,0:06:24.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have no right to talk about her!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.44,0:06:24.95,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Go back!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.95,0:06:28.24,Default,Otto,0000,0000,0000,,You still don't understand how \Nterrifying the White Whale is?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.24,0:06:32.14,Default,Otto,0000,0000,0000,,When a punitive force, assembled by \NLugunica, set out to subjugate it,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.14,0:06:35.30,Default,Otto,0000,0000,0000,,that monster killed\Nthe first Master Swordsman!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.30,0:06:36.67,Default,Otto,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way we can win!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.61,0:06:40.43,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,It killed... the Master Swordsman?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.72,0:06:44.38,Default,Otto,0000,0000,0000,,I'm weak, and you are, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.38,0:06:47.81,Default,Otto,0000,0000,0000,,So there's no way we can save that girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.90,0:06:53.85,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,But I know Rem isn't actually strong, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.64,0:06:58.44,Default,Otto,0000,0000,0000,,For now, we were fortunate to escape it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.44,0:07:01.48,Default,Otto,0000,0000,0000,,But in this mist, there's no telling \Nwhen it'll show up again.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.81,0:07:05.59,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Otto, watch what you say!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.59,0:07:07.29,Default,Otto,0000,0000,0000,,Eh? What do you mean, Natsuki-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.29,0:07:09.53,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Don't talk like this is some game!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.53,0:07:10.90,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,We were "fortunate"?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.28,0:07:12.84,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,You must be joking...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.84,0:07:15.66,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know how Rem felt when she—
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.66,0:07:17.75,Default,Otto,0000,0000,0000,,Who is Rem?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.75,0:07:18.41,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.73,0:07:22.50,Default,Otto,0000,0000,0000,,There wasn't anyone with that name
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.50,0:07:25.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,among the merchants who broke off from us.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.25,0:07:27.31,Default,Otto,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.96,0:07:35.89,Default,Otto,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think you're doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.89,0:07:37.49,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Cut the crap...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.49,0:07:39.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You talk about how Rem let us escape,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.98,0:07:41.89,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,and then ask who she is?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.89,0:07:43.40,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Do you have a death wish?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.40,0:07:46.32,Default,Otto,0000,0000,0000,,I'm telling you, I don't know \Nwhat you're talking about...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.60,0:07:49.16,Default,Otto,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you suddenly talking like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.16,0:07:51.65,Default,Otto,0000,0000,0000,,Did seeing the White Whale \Nmake you lose your mind?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.43,0:08:03.60,Default,Otto,0000,0000,0000,,Why? Why? Why is it so persistent?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.60,0:08:05.58,Default,Otto,0000,0000,0000,,I thought we'd left it behind!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.37,0:08:11.85,Default,Otto,0000,0000,0000,,Why is it only after us?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.85,0:08:15.05,Default,Otto,0000,0000,0000,,Even in this darkness... Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.05,0:08:15.59,Default,Otto,0000,0000,0000,,Rem...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.59,0:08:19.47,Default,Otto,0000,0000,0000,,Is... Is there some mark it's following?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.46,0:08:21.57,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,It can't be.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.11,0:08:25.53,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,That monster, the White Whale...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.56,0:08:29.45,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,It's a mabeast, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.57,0:08:34.43,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Then, it's being drawn to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.82,0:08:36.14,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,No way.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.28,0:08:41.44,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Rem, I... No...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.44,0:08:43.22,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,It's my fault!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.85,0:08:47.49,Default,Otto,0000,0000,0000,,Natsuki-san, please die.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.83,0:08:48.46,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.28,0:08:54.26,Default,Otto,0000,0000,0000,,It's all your fault!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.26,0:08:56.52,Default,Otto,0000,0000,0000,,I-It's following us because of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.52,0:08:59.27,Default,Otto,0000,0000,0000,,T-Take responsibility!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.27,0:09:02.73,Default,Otto,0000,0000,0000,,Die! Die, so that I can live!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.90,0:09:31.63,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,I don't wanna die...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.91,0:09:36.02,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,No... I don't wanna die...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.59,0:09:39.71,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Help... I don't wanna die!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.20,0:09:42.41,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,I don't wanna die! I don't wanna die!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.41,0:09:43.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't wanna die!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.92,0:09:45.72,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,No! No!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.72,0:09:47.24,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.24,0:09:49.51,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,No! I don't wanna die!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.19,0:09:55.49,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,I don't wanna die...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.35,0:10:11.04,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.87,0:10:18.88,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Rem...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.02,0:10:22.66,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Rem, forgive me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.32,0:10:30.52,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,You're...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.46,0:10:35.98,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Where is he? Where's Otto?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.73,0:10:40.27,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.89,0:10:47.99,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.26,0:11:09.56,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,The forest?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.17,0:11:15.22,Default,Petra,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Subaru?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.46,0:11:20.61,Default,Mildo,0000,0000,0000,,It is Subaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.59,0:11:23.17,Default,Dyne,0000,0000,0000,,What happened to you, Subaru?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.19,0:11:27.64,Default,Lucas,0000,0000,0000,,You're a mess, Subaru. You stink!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.72,0:11:32.11,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,You guys...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.88,0:11:37.12,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,I wasn't too late this time?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.96,0:11:41.14,Default,Petra,0000,0000,0000,,Subaru?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.11,0:11:57.93,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Rem—
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.97,0:12:03.07,Default,Ram,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you so eagerly touching me, Barusu?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.48,0:12:06.48,Default,Ram,0000,0000,0000,,I understand that, after a few days \Naway, you're happy to see me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.48,0:12:09.12,Default,Ram,0000,0000,0000,,But don't instinctively jump on me like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.12,0:12:09.96,Default,Ram,0000,0000,0000,,It's indecent.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.28,0:12:13.58,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Oh... Yeah, that's right...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.20,0:12:17.04,Default,Ram,0000,0000,0000,,So, Barusu, tell me what happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.15,0:12:19.85,Default,Ram,0000,0000,0000,,You were in terrible shape.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.85,0:12:23.89,Default,Ram,0000,0000,0000,,Your dislocated shoulder, split forehead, \Nand broken ribs have been mended.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.89,0:12:25.70,Default,Ram,0000,0000,0000,,But if you move too much, they'll reopen
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.09,0:12:28.60,Default,Ram,0000,0000,0000,,I've discarded your muddy,\Nblood-soaked clothes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.60,0:12:30.54,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.99,0:12:34.20,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,The one who healed my wounds...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.72,0:12:35.85,Default,Ram,0000,0000,0000,,It was Emilia-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.86,0:12:44.64,Default,Ram,0000,0000,0000,,She didn't tell me what happened \Nin the capital between you two.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.64,0:12:45.53,Default,Ram,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not interested.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.37,0:12:47.88,Default,Ram,0000,0000,0000,,Judging by her reaction,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.88,0:12:50.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure you did something you shouldn't have.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.39,0:12:51.86,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,That's harsh.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.86,0:12:54.07,Default,Ram,0000,0000,0000,,I think it's an appropriate assessment.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.07,0:12:56.51,Default,Ram,0000,0000,0000,,Perfect for a loser, afraid to approach
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.51,0:13:00.11,Default,Ram,0000,0000,0000,,the heart of the matter, who'd do \Nanything to put it off a little.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.06,0:13:09.89,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Rem is dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.80,0:13:13.52,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,I... couldn't do anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.98,0:13:17.77,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,The fog... the White Whale... \Nappeared on the road.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.77,0:13:21.11,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,So, to cover my escape, Rem...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.44,0:13:25.17,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,But... I was left alone in the fog.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.71,0:13:26.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.71,0:13:27.55,Default,Ram,0000,0000,0000,,Barusu...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.55,0:13:30.33,Default,Ram,0000,0000,0000,,Rem...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.01,0:13:33.16,Default,Ram,0000,0000,0000,,Who is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.34,0:13:36.08,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.76,0:13:39.50,Default,Ram,0000,0000,0000,,Who is Rem, Barusu?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.50,0:13:41.36,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What do you mean, "who"?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.36,0:13:42.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be ridiculous...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.80,0:13:45.18,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Sh-She's your younger sister!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.18,0:13:47.45,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,You know, Rem! Rem... Rem!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.45,0:13:48.56,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,This is no time for—
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.56,0:13:49.93,Default,Ram,0000,0000,0000,,I have no younger sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.93,0:13:52.88,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Don't say that! If not for Rem...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.88,0:13:54.25,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.25,0:13:57.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What would you call that whole \Nmess in the mabeast forest?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.10,0:13:59.54,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,You, Rem, and I fought those mabeasts and—
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.54,0:14:01.82,Default,Ram,0000,0000,0000,,Something is seriously wrong with you, Barusu.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.22,0:14:03.70,Default,Ram,0000,0000,0000,,I hate to admit it,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.70,0:14:07.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but you were half-responsible \Nfor the ulgarm eradication.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.45,0:14:10.49,Default,Ram,0000,0000,0000,,Roswaal-sama and I handled the rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.28,0:14:15.62,Default,Ram,0000,0000,0000,,This long-lost sister you call \N"Rem" has no place in it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.98,0:14:19.28,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,That's not funny.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.28,0:14:21.83,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Even for a nightmare, this doesn't make sense!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.83,0:14:24.18,Default,Ram,0000,0000,0000,,I am always serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.18,0:14:26.13,Default,Ram,0000,0000,0000,,You must be the one who's dreaming.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.47,0:14:29.08,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Dreaming... Dreaming?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.81,0:14:31.22,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Dreaming?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.57,0:14:32.89,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,That's bull!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.32,0:14:34.78,Default,Ram,0000,0000,0000,,Barusu, you shouldn't stand—
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.78,0:14:38.13,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up! Just... Just be quiet and watch!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.08,0:14:47.90,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,It can't be...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.94,0:14:50.91,Default,Ram,0000,0000,0000,,Barusu, are you satisfied?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.11,0:14:54.14,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Rem isn't...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.59,0:14:57.59,Default,Ram,0000,0000,0000,,No such person has ever lived in this room.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.28,0:15:05.55,Default - flashback,Ram,0000,0000,0000,,Go back to your room and sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.60,0:15:08.59,Default - flashback,Ram,0000,0000,0000,,Your exhaustion is making you confused.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.72,0:15:15.90,Default - italics,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,All I have to do is run away, \Nrun away, run away.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.29,0:15:21.14,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,What good will running do?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.25,0:15:33.41,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Lend me your courage, Rem!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.02,0:15:43.21,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,Subaru?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.00,0:15:48.88,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,Why...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.97,0:15:51.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,did you come back?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.57,0:15:55.22,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.80,0:15:57.64,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,We can't stay here!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.64,0:15:59.58,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,Go? Where?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.58,0:16:01.34,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,No... Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.34,0:16:03.78,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Anywhere that isn't here!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.78,0:16:07.60,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,If you have to ask why,\NI'd say, "For your sake."
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.60,0:16:09.24,Default,Subabu,0000,0000,0000,,I came back for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.24,0:16:11.41,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,That again, Subaru?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.41,0:16:14.87,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,You came back, covered in wounds,\Nand worried me to death.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.87,0:16:18.02,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,Weren't you in the capital \Nso Felis could treat you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.02,0:16:20.72,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you here now?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.18,0:16:21.71,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,If...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.05,0:16:24.66,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,If you protest, I'll drag you away, if I must!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.66,0:16:28.16,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,In a few days, you'll see I was right, \Nwhether you want to or not!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.16,0:16:28.67,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,So just...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.67,0:16:30.58,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,Wait! Wait, Subaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.58,0:16:31.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.72,0:16:33.89,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,You weren't this kind of person before.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.89,0:16:36.05,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,I thought you... And yet—
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.05,0:16:39.26,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Just be quiet, and do as I say!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.76,0:16:41.71,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,You can't stay here!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.71,0:16:44.10,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,You'll regret it... You will!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.10,0:16:45.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No one will be saved.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.42,0:16:48.23,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to suffer and cry anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.56,0:16:51.05,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Just do as I say!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.05,0:16:54.46,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Then everything will work out! It will!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.46,0:16:57.31,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Why doesn't anyone understand?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.97,0:16:59.23,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.23,0:17:03.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't understand what you're saying...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.69,0:17:05.61,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,I want to.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.61,0:17:10.33,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,But right now, I'm not sure \NI have time for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.33,0:17:13.09,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,There's so much I need to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.43,0:17:14.71,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,So for now...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.51,0:17:17.27,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,It won't work.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.72,0:17:20.20,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,It won't work.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.20,0:17:22.36,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,You won't work. You'll fail!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.36,0:17:24.79,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,You can't do it. It's no use.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.79,0:17:27.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're all talk! You can't save \Nanyone, or be saved!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.45,0:17:29.29,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,You'll keep acting rashly and unreasonably,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.29,0:17:32.78,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,until you see as many corpses as the \Nnumber of your reckless decisions!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.78,0:17:34.79,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,That is your future!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.56,0:17:36.57,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.78,0:17:41.89,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you crying, as if you're in such pain?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.13,0:17:48.89,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,After... After she sent me here...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.89,0:17:52.56,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,No, after she brought me here, there's...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.56,0:17:55.95,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,There's something I must do for Rem's sake...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.95,0:17:57.01,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,Rem?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.87,0:18:01.02,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,You, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.46,0:18:04.20,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,You've forgotten Rem, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.20,0:18:04.77,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,Subaru?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.35,0:18:09.55,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Fine, I'll tell you everything...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.09,0:18:13.16,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,If you all are going to forget Rem,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.16,0:18:17.11,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,I'd rather expose everything \Nand end up vomiting blood!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.11,0:18:18.45,Default - italics,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,If you're coming for me, then come.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.12,0:18:21.47,Default - italics,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,I'll gladly give you my beating heart!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.06,0:18:25.20,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Emilia...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.22,0:18:26.97,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.99,0:18:32.02,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,I can use Return by Death to—
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.56,0:18:55.20,Default - italics,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,What was that about?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.20,0:18:56.15,Default - italics,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Usually...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.16,0:18:58.99,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.93,0:19:01.87,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Emilia?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.46,0:19:09.93,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Don't... Wha— Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.79,0:19:39.94,Default,Beatrice,0000,0000,0000,,You have the look of someone who believes \Nhe's the world's most unfortunate soul.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.96,0:19:43.62,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Beatrice...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.95,0:19:47.46,Default,Beatrice,0000,0000,0000,,Bubby won't come out, I suppose.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.65,0:19:56.71,Default,Beatrice,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry. Bubby won't die, I suppose.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.42,0:20:00.50,Default,Beatrice,0000,0000,0000,,He just returned to his\Noriginal form for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.44,0:20:04.79,Default,Beatrice,0000,0000,0000,,You have something you want to say, I suppose?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.92,0:20:10.98,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Please kill me. Right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.23,0:20:15.92,Default,Beatrice,0000,0000,0000,,You would ask me to kill you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.92,0:20:18.08,Default,Beatrice,0000,0000,0000,,That's too cruel, I suppose.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.40,0:20:21.15,Default,Beatrice,0000,0000,0000,,You understand nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.50,0:20:23.95,Default,Beatrice,0000,0000,0000,,You understand nothing at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.95,0:20:26.22,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Beatrice?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.22,0:20:30.22,Default,Beatrice,0000,0000,0000,,I won't grant any of your wishes, I suppose.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.22,0:20:33.87,Default,Beatrice,0000,0000,0000,,If you want to die, then die on your own.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.87,0:20:35.92,Default,Beatrice,0000,0000,0000,,Betty wants no part of it, I suppose.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.08,0:20:39.31,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,What are you...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.31,0:20:41.92,Default,Beatrice,0000,0000,0000,,Everything is already hopeless,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.92,0:20:44.22,Default,Beatrice,0000,0000,0000,,but your staying here is a problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.76,0:20:47.73,Default,Beatrice,0000,0000,0000,,I will, at least,\Nprotect the mansion, I suppose.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.41,0:20:52.54,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Beatrice?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.24,0:20:55.87,Default,Beatrice,0000,0000,0000,,Betty is not like Roswaal.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.87,0:20:58.16,Default,Beatrice,0000,0000,0000,,Even if it would secure a future for me,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.16,0:21:00.92,Default,Beatrice,0000,0000,0000,,I've had enough of pain, suffering, fear...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.92,0:21:02.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everything, I suppose!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.71,0:21:13.25,Default,Beatrice,0000,0000,0000,,At least die where I can't see you, I suppose.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.92,0:21:27.44,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Emilia...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.79,0:21:35.02,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry... I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.42,0:21:36.06,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.74,0:21:39.63,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.56,0:21:44.77,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Someone... Anyone...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.64,0:21:50.74,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Please kill me!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.68,0:22:03.51,Default,Betel,0000,0000,0000,,I've been waiting for you, believer in love.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.57,0:22:07.27,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Betelgeuse...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.69,0:22:09.33,Default,Betel,0000,0000,0000,,My, my, my...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.33,0:22:12.53,Default,Betel,0000,0000,0000,,The one you clutch to your chest there
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.53,0:22:15.29,Default,Betel,0000,0000,0000,,wouldn't be the half-devil girl, would it?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.29,0:22:17.64,Default,Betel,0000,0000,0000,,How diligent you are!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.64,0:22:20.09,Default,Betel,0000,0000,0000,,Before we could even act,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.09,0:22:22.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you took the half-devil's life, \Nin the Ordeal's name!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.62,0:22:25.49,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,I'm diligent?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.68,0:22:27.32,Default,Betel,0000,0000,0000,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.32,0:22:31.81,Default,Betel,0000,0000,0000,,You are diligent! Fantastic!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.96,0:22:34.47,Default,Betel,0000,0000,0000,,Still...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.47,0:22:36.94,Default,Betel,0000,0000,0000,,Unable to overcome even one Ordeal,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.94,0:22:39.96,Default,Betel,0000,0000,0000,,much less to confront one of the sins,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.96,0:22:41.88,Default,Betel,0000,0000,0000,,and after all that waiting...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.88,0:22:45.84,Default,Betel,0000,0000,0000,,She trips over the first pebble \Nin her path, and it's over...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.84,0:22:47.88,Default,Betel,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, you are
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.51,0:22:50.59,Default,Betel,0000,0000,0000,,truly slothful...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.04,0:23:05.46,Default,Betel,0000,0000,0000,,You saw the Unseen Hand just now?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.11,0:23:08.17,Default,Betel,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.83,0:23:10.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.93,0:23:13.10,Default,Betel,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't right! It's all wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.10,0:23:16.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a mistake! A mistake!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.59,0:23:20.96,Default,Betel,0000,0000,0000,,My Authority...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.96,0:23:22.99,Default,Betel,0000,0000,0000,,The Authority of Sloth...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.99,0:23:27.29,Default,Betel,0000,0000,0000,,My Unseen Hand, which love granted to me...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.29,0:23:34.05,Default,Betel,0000,0000,0000,,No other can be allowed to see it!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.28,0:23:45.87,Default,Betel,0000,0000,0000,,You held her, as if she were \Nterribly precious to you...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.87,0:23:52.97,Default,Betel,0000,0000,0000,,But when the half-devil's body is torn \Napart, how beautifully will you cry?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.96,0:23:58.83,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Stop...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.68,0:24:01.30,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.42,0:24:08.09,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Please stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.85,0:24:16.39,Default,Puck,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.74,0:24:23.60,Default,Puck,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing to my daughter,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.60,0:24:27.05,Default,Puck,0000,0000,0000,,you scum?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.82,0:24:35.82,Episode Title,Title,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HC6C6C6&}Dis{\c&HFFFFFF&}grace in the Extreme
